sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant KubeAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster<br/>Controller
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization<br/>Controller
    participant SecretGen as SecretGenerator<br/>Controller
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP
    participant Components as Component Pods

    Note over Admin,Components: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation & Component Deployment

    Admin->>KubeAPI: kubectl apply -f dsc.yaml<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    KubeAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-datasciencecluster<br/>mTLS (K8s API client cert)
    Webhook-->>KubeAPI: Validation response<br/>(ensure single DSC, valid config)
    KubeAPI-->>Admin: CR created

    KubeAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event: DSC created
    DSCCtrl->>DSCCtrl: Begin reconciliation loop

    loop For each enabled component
        DSCCtrl->>KubeAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>/opt/manifests/{component}/<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
        KubeAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Resources created
        DSCCtrl->>KubeAPI: Create Deployments, Services,<br/>Routes, ConfigMaps, RBAC, CRDs<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    end

    Note over Admin,Components: Flow 2: DSCInitialization - Platform Bootstrap

    DSCICtrl->>KubeAPI: Check for DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    KubeAPI-->>DSCICtrl: CR found/not found

    DSCICtrl->>KubeAPI: Create platform namespaces<br/>redhat-ods-applications, redhat-ods-monitoring

    alt Service Mesh Managed
        DSCICtrl->>KubeAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane,<br/>ServiceMeshMember CRs
    end

    alt Monitoring Managed
        DSCICtrl->>KubeAPI: Deploy Prometheus, Alertmanager,<br/>Blackbox Exporter to monitoring namespace
    end

    DSCICtrl->>KubeAPI: Apply NetworkPolicies<br/>to operator, monitoring, applications namespaces

    Note over Admin,Components: Flow 3: Secret Generation - OAuth Client Provisioning

    DSCCtrl->>KubeAPI: Apply component manifest<br/>with secret-generator annotation
    KubeAPI->>SecretGen: Watch event: Secret created
    SecretGen->>SecretGen: Generate random credentials
    SecretGen->>OAuth: Create OAuth client<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    OAuth-->>SecretGen: Client ID/Secret
    SecretGen->>KubeAPI: Create target secret<br/>with generated values

    Note over Admin,Components: Flow 4: Monitoring - Metrics Collection

    loop Metrics scraping
        Prom->>DSCCtrl: GET /metrics (8080/TCP HTTP)<br/>Auth: None (internal)
        DSCCtrl-->>Prom: Controller metrics
        Prom->>Components: GET /metrics (varies)<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
        Components-->>Prom: Component metrics
    end

    Admin->>OAuth: Access Prometheus Route<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: User credentials
    OAuth-->>Admin: Session cookie
    Admin->>Prom: GET /graph<br/>HTTP/9090 (via oauth-proxy)<br/>Auth: Session cookie
    Prom-->>Admin: Prometheus UI
